s-string\">&quot;,&quot;</span>empty-tag<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;:&quot;</span>目前没有标签<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;,&quot;</span>pinned<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;:&quot;</span>置顶<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;,&quot;</span>featured<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;:&quot;</span>推荐<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&#125;&#125;&#x27;</span>)<br>    &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>好消息是这个最近评论只有这一个地方出现过。</p>\n<p>坏消息是这个json之后做了什么也不得而知。</p>\n<p>先尝试第一步，修改一下文本内容看看生不生效</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Del%20Comment/(4).png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>重启一下看看效果</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Del%20Comment/(5).png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>很好，已经修改成功了。下一步就是把他干掉</p></blockquote>\n<p>这个评论内容在json中的key是recent_comment</p>\n<p>全局搜索哪里用到了这个字段</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Del%20Comment/(6).png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>发现了这么一段代码，方法名是ie.继续找哪里用到了ie</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Del%20Comment/(7).png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>直接注掉这行代码。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Del%20Comment/(8).png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>重启之后成功删除</p>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/Del%20Comment/(9).png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"注意 本文来自于gongxuanzhang原作者写于2022年11月9日LuiYang有一定的改动 hexo Aurora 去掉评论区问题：评论侧边栏今天刚搭建...","permalink":"/post/Del Comment","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.9k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"blog","slug":"blog","count":4,"path":"api/categories/blog.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"个人建站","slug":"个人建站","count":6,"path":"api/tags/个人建站.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#hexo-Aurora-%E5%8E%BB%E6%8E%89%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8C%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">hexo Aurora 去掉评论区</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E4%BE%A7%E8%BE%B9%E6%A0%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">问题：评论侧边栏</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解决</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"LuiYang","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://pic.superbed.cc/item/675c6b0efa9f77b4dc5da666.jpg","link":"/","description":"<p>与其临渊羡鱼，不如退而结网</p>one should take practical steps achieve one's aim","socials":{"github":"https://github.